Receipt:

1. Imagine the worst possible implementation of reply-to adding and
   enumerate all its disadvantages.

2. Do not mention anything about what useful is expected from reply-to
   adding.

3. Neglect that the ones that are annoyed by reply mistakes are not the
   same than the ones that do reply mistakes.

4. Repeat step 1.

You get `"Reply-To" Munging Considered Harmful'.

